        <num>CC 2513</num>
        <heading>2513.  Scope of warranty in sale of succession rights</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2513.  Scope of warranty in sale of succession rights
In a sale of a right of succession, the warranty against eviction extends only to the right to succeed the decedent, which entitles the buyer to those things that are, in fact, a part of the estate, but it does not extend to any particular thing.</p>
        </content>
